Symbios Logic 53C8xx SCSI Host Adapter Driver

This driver supports Symbios Logic (formerly NCR) 53C8xx family PCI SCSI
host adapters.

Supported Models:
- NCR 53C810/810A (PCI - Fast SCSI)
- NCR 53C815 (PCI - Fast SCSI)
- NCR 53C825/825A (PCI - Fast Wide SCSI)
- NCR 53C860 (PCI - Ultra SCSI)
- NCR 53C875 (PCI - Ultra Wide SCSI)
- NCR 53C895 (PCI - Ultra2 Wide SCSI)

Features:
- PCI bus interface
- Up to 7 SCSI devices (15 with Wide SCSI)
- Scatter/Gather DMA support
- Interrupt-driven I/O
- Automatic request sense
- SCSI bus reset capability

Configuration:
The driver auto-detects the controller on the PCI bus.
IRQ and I/O ports are automatically assigned by the PCI BIOS.
Default adapter SCSI ID: 7
Valid IRQ levels: 9, 10, 11, 12, 14, 15
